  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/f77c3a54a95119035b712fa9d4f70879.avif?t=1725286397\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Chess Dungeons is a Puzzle game that combines Chess mechanics and Sokoban-style gameplay for chess lovers and beginners.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/9f87ff912cb6ba411d46c45a1770ef00.avif?t=1725286397\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>While featuring classic Chess gameplay, enjoy playing with models that give character to every single chess piece. Control your units and make sure you come out victorious.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/61f721fda97c037b637eec4a47049fd1.avif?t=1725286397\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>In classic Chess fashion, sometimes in order to advance, you must sacrifice your pieces to lure the enemy out and advance into the dungeon.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/fadda4aa2d62cef5bf9c96bc5bd0c4fb.avif?t=1725286397\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/3eb12bc8e65e560cec7852641431e6b0.avif?t=1725286397\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Don't lose focus! Your goal is to slay the enemy's King. While other pieces can (and sometimes should!) be targeted, your main focus is to eliminate the King.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/61758efb196acadd2a881b8f7604551e.poster.avif?t=1725286397\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/61758efb196acadd2a881b8f7604551e.webm?t=1725286397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/61758efb196acadd2a881b8f7604551e.mp4?t=1725286397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/186004c7bfde6979fb6e9e2fe276a29f.avif?t=1725286397\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>A harder challenge! Don't just target the enemy King. Wipe out all of the black pieces!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/67e7ab975eacd272fc592f0b186a8f4d.poster.avif?t=1725286397\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/67e7ab975eacd272fc592f0b186a8f4d.webm?t=1725286397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/67e7ab975eacd272fc592f0b186a8f4d.mp4?t=1725286397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/f77c3a54a95119035b712fa9d4f70879.avif?t=1725286397\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Chess Dungeons is a Puzzle game that combines Chess mechanics and Sokoban-style gameplay for chess lovers and beginners.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/9f87ff912cb6ba411d46c45a1770ef00.avif?t=1725286397\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>While featuring classic Chess gameplay, enjoy playing with models that give character to every single chess piece. Control your units and make sure you come out victorious.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/61f721fda97c037b637eec4a47049fd1.avif?t=1725286397\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>In classic Chess fashion, sometimes in order to advance, you must sacrifice your pieces to lure the enemy out and advance into the dungeon.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/fadda4aa2d62cef5bf9c96bc5bd0c4fb.avif?t=1725286397\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/3eb12bc8e65e560cec7852641431e6b0.avif?t=1725286397\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Don't lose focus! Your goal is to slay the enemy's King. While other pieces can (and sometimes should!) be targeted, your main focus is to eliminate the King.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/61758efb196acadd2a881b8f7604551e.poster.avif?t=1725286397\" widt